<div class="section-title" data-topic="A1">Das Alphabet</div>
<div class="section-content">
  <p>Das französische Alphabet hat 26 Buchstaben. Ihre Namen und ihre Aussprache unterscheiden sich teilweise vom Deutschen.</p>
  <table>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">a</span> <span class="ipa">\a\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">j</span> <span class="ipa">\ʒi\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">s</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛs\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">b</span> <span class="ipa">\be\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">k</span> <span class="ipa">\ka\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">t</span> <span class="ipa">\te\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">c</span> <span class="ipa">\se\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">l</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛl\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">u</span> <span class="ipa">\y\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">d</span> <span class="ipa">\de\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">m</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛm\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">v</span> <span class="ipa">\ve\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">e</span> <span class="ipa">\ə\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">n</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛn\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">w</span> <span class="ipa">\dubləve\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">f</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛf\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">o</span> <span class="ipa">\o\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">x</span> <span class="ipa">\iks\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">g</span> <span class="ipa">\ʒe\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">p</span> <span class="ipa">\pe\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">y</span> <span class="ipa">\igrɛk\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">h</span> <span class="ipa">\aʃ\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">q</span> <span class="ipa">\ky\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">z</span> <span class="ipa">\zɛd\</span></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">i</span> <span class="ipa">\i\</span></td>
        <td><span class="fr force-audio">r</span> <span class="ipa">\ɛr\</span></td>
        <td></td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>
  <p>Zusätzlich gibt es orthografische Zeichen: die drei <a grammar="Der Akzent">Akzente</a> (<b>accent aigu</b> ´, <b>accent grave</b> `, <b>accent circonflexe</b> ^), die <a grammar="Cedille, Apostroph und Trema"><b>Cedille</b> (ç) und das <b>Trema</b> (¨)</a>.</p>
  <p>Die Buchstaben k und w kommen hauptsächlich in Fremdwörtern vor.</p>
  <div class="examples">
    <div class="fr force-audio">le <u>k</u>ilo</div>
    <div class="de spoiler">das Kilo</div>
    <div class="fr force-audio">le <u>w</u>eek-end</div>
    <div class="de spoiler">das Wochenende</div>
  </div>
</div>
